<div class="section" id="modern" data-landmark data-offset="130" data-offset-tablet="160" data-offset-mobile="130">
  <div class="container container--strict">

    <div class="static">
      <div class="static__inner">
        <h2>High-strength, modern amphibian aircraft LA-8</h2>
        <h3>The avionics and equipment, parts and components available in any country of the
          world are used in airframe and in aircraft systems.</h3>
        <p>The hoses, fittings, pipeline accessories and flexible hoses manufactured in accordance
          with AN and MS international standards are used in fuel, oil, hydraulic and brake systems. The aircraft can be
          delivered to Customer either with single or with dual control.</p>

        <div class="gallery-slider__wrapper">
          <div class="swiper-container gallery-slider js-gallery-slider">
            <div class="swiper-wrapper">
              {{#times 5}}
                <div class="swiper-slide gallery-slide js-image-loading">
                  {{>components/image ext="png" img="news/news-single/news_2"}}
                </div>
              {{/times}}
            </div>
            <button class="gallery-slider__next"></button>
            <button class="gallery-slider__prev"></button>
            <div class="gallery-slider__pagination"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="stats stats--full">
          <div class="stats__inner">
            {{>blocks/stats-card title='8 seats' text='in the salon' icon='seat'}}
            {{>blocks/stats-card title='4000 km' text='range of flight' icon='range'}}
            {{>blocks/stats-card title='270 km' text='maximum speed' icon='speed'}}
            {{>blocks/stats-card title='1685 kg' text='weight of base model' icon='weight'}}
          </div>
        </div>

        <p>The hoses, fittings, pipeline accessories and flexible hoses manufactured in
          accordance
          with AN and MS international standards are used in fuel, oil, hydraulic and brake systems. The aircraft
          can be
          delivered to Customer either with single or with dual control.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
